# UI Rules (Ant Design)

- Use Ant Design components; customize with ConfigProvider theme tokens.
- Layout: Grid (Row/Col) and Layout for dashboards; Space for spacing.
- Forms: Form + Input components with validation; submit via onFinish.
- Feedback: message/notification for success/error; Spin for loading.
- Drawers: placement=\right\, maskClosable=false for critical edits.
- Tables: pagination, rowKey, responsive columns; virtualize long lists when needed.

